name: Aster Staked BNB
description: Aster is a decentralized perpetual exchange built for everyone. It offers MEV-free, one-click trading with up to 1001x leverage in Simple Mode, and full-featured, pro-grade tools in Pro Mode. Backed by YZi Labs, Aster is building the future of DeFi: fast, flexible, and community-first. Aster's asBNB is a BNB liquid staking derivative that accrue rewards from Binance Launchpools, HODLer airdrops and Megadrops.
